      <title>乐购供应商Bakkavor拒绝Greencore的11亿英镑出价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/tesco-supplier-bakkavor-rejects-greencore-s-1-14-billion-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Bakkavor Group PLC拒绝了爱尔兰便利食品制造商Greencore Group plc的现金和股票竞标，其价值为11.4亿英镑（15亿美元）。]]></description>
